name: Branching Time (The End and The Beginning)
description: This series of works are made from a 15 day time-lapse photogrammetry of a flower arrangement. Over time, some flowers bloom and wilt, others grow limp, and still others hold fast. Each piece is a combination of days, mixing forms across time. This work contains the scan of day 1 and day 15, combining new life and complete collapse.  3000x3000 px 2021
